===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Hop (Masters)}}
Hop, based on the [[rival]] from {{pkmn|Sword and Shield|Sword}}, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{form|Zamazenta|Crowned Shield}} {{p|Zamazenta}}, {{rf|Galarian}} {{p|Zapdos}}, {{p|Rillaboom}}, {{p|Pincurchin}}, and {{form|Zacian|Crowned Sword}} {{p|Zacian}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Rillaboom is capable of [[Dynamax]]ing. Hop became a playable sync pair on August 12, 2021.

Hop has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]].

